"library_AboutLibraries_libraryDescription" : "AboutLibraries is a library to offer you all the information you need of your libraries!

Most modern apps feature an Used Library-Section and for this some information of those libs is required. As it gets annoying to copy those strings always to your app I have developed this small helper library to provide the required information."
"library_ActionBarPullToRefresh_libraryDescription" : "ActionBar-PullToRefresh provides an easy way to add a modern version of the pull-to-refresh interaction to your application."

"library_ActionBarSherlock_libraryDescription" : "ActionBarSherlock is an standalone library designed to facilitate the use of the action bar design pattern across all versions of Android through a single API."
"library_ActiveAndroid_libraryDescription" : "ActiveAndroid is an active record style ORM (object relational mapper)."

"library_AndroidIconics_libraryDescription" : "This library allows you to include vector icons everywhere in your project. No limits are given. Scale with no limit, use any Color at any time, provide a contour, and many additional customizations"
"library_AndroidTimesSquare_libraryDescription" : "Standalone Android widget for picking a single date from a calendar view."
"library_AndroidViewPagerIndicator_libraryDescription" : "Paging indicator widgets that are compatible with the ViewPager from the Android Support Library to improve discoverability of content."

"library_AppCompat_libraryDescription" : "This library adds support for the Action Bar user interface design pattern. This library includes support for material design user interface implementations."
"library_Butterknife_libraryDescription" : "Field and method binding for Android views which uses annotation processing to generate boilerplate code for you."
"library_CircularImageView_libraryDescription" : "Custom view for circular images in Android while maintaining the best draw performance"
"library_ClansFloatingActionButton_libraryDescription" : "Yet another implementation of Floating Action Button for Android with lots of features."
"library_Crashlytics_libraryDescription" : "The Crashlytics Kit for Android provides simple APIs for reporting crashes."
"library_Crouton_libraryDescription" : "Crouton is a class that can be used by Android developers that feel the need for an alternative to the Context insensitive Toast."
"library_Dagger2_libraryDescription" : "A fast dependency injector for Android and Java."
"library_Dagger_libraryDescription" : "A fast dependency injector for Android and Java."

"library_ErrorView_libraryDescription" : "A custom view that displays an error image, a title, and a subtitle given an HTTP status code. It can be used for various other purposes like displaying other kinds of errors, or just messages with images."
"library_Eventbus_libraryDescription" : "EventBus is an Android optimized publish/subscribe event bus."

"library_FButton_libraryDescription" : "FButton is a custom Button of Android with Flat UI concept. FButton's design get inspiration from designmono. This library is very small and highly customizable."

"library_FloatingActionButton_libraryDescription" : "Android Google+ like floating action button which reacts on the list view scrolling events. Becomes visible when the list view is scrolled up and invisible when scrolled down."

"library_GooglePlayServices_libraryDescription" : "With Google Play services, your app can take advantage of the latest, Google-powered features such as Maps, Google+, and more, with automatic platform updates distributed as an APK through the Google Play store."

"library_HoloGraphLibrary_libraryDescription" : "This library is an open-source set of graph types that are easy to add to your app, and in addition, look gorgeous. Themed in the much-loved Holo style of Android, the graphing library should fit in with any of your modern, standards-compliant apps."
"library_JavaAesCrypto_libraryDescription" : "A simple Android class for encrypting & decrypting strings, aiming to avoid the classic mistakes that most such classes suffer from."

"library_Jsoup_libraryDescription" : "jsoup is a Java library for working with real-world HTML. It provides a very convenient API for extracting and manipulating data, using the best of DOM, CSS, and jquery-like methods."
"library_LeakCanary_libraryDescription" : "A memory leak detection library for Android and Java."
"library_LoganSquare_libraryDescription" : "Screaming fast JSON parsing and serialization library for Android."
"library_MarkView_libraryDescription" : "An android custom view that displays a circle with a colored arc given a mark."

"library_MaterialRangeBar_libraryDescription" : "MaterialRangeBar is a fork of https://github.com/edmodo/range-bar that adds some basic material styling, as well as start and end values, values as floats and some other things."
"library_MaterialishProgress_libraryDescription" : "A material style progress wheel compatible with 2.3."
"library_NanoTasks_libraryDescription" : "Extremely light way to execute code in the background on Android. Alternative to AsyncTask."
"library_NineOldAndroids_libraryDescription" : "Android library for using the Honeycomb (Android 3.0) animation API on all versions of the platform back to 1.0!"
"library_OkHttp_libraryDescription" : "An HTTP and SPDY client for Android and Java applications"
"library_Otto_libraryDescription" : "Otto is an enhanced event bus with emphasis on Android support."
"library_PagerSlidingTabStrip_libraryDescription" : "Interactive paging indicator widget, compatible with the ViewPager from the Android Support Library."

"library_Paper_libraryDescription" : "Paper is a fast NoSQL data storage for Android that lets you save/restore Java objects by using efficient Kryo serialization and handling data structure changes automatically."
"library_Picasso_libraryDescription" : "A powerful image downloading and caching library for Android."
"library_ProcessPhoenix_libraryDescription" : "Process Phoenix facilitates restarting your application process."

"library_QuickReturn_libraryDescription" : "QuickReturn is a library which showcases the QuickReturn UI Pattern. The QuickReturn UI Pattern reveals or hides a header or footer as content is scrolled up or down."
"library_RealmRecyclerView_libraryDescription" : "A powerful Recyclerview wrapper for working with Realm as your datastore."
"library_RealmSearchView_libraryDescription" : "A simple and powerful EditText and RecyclerView UI component. It's build on top of RealmRecyclerView and RealmBasedRecyclerViewAdapter."
"library_Realm_libraryDescription" : "Realm is a mobile database: a replacement for SQLite & ORMs"

"library_RecyclerRenderers_libraryDescription" : "The easiest way to create adapters! You can add a lot of different layouts and models. This library avoid all the boilerplates needed to create a list for your application."
"library_Retrofit_libraryDescription" : "A type-safe REST client for Android and Java."
"library_RxBinding_libraryDescription" : "RxJava binding APIs for Android's UI widgets."

"library_ShowcaseView_libraryDescription" : "The ShowcaseView library is designed to highlight and showcase specific parts of apps to the user with a distinctive and attractive overlay. This library is great for pointing out points of interest for users, gestures, or obscure but useful items."

"library_SupportLibrary_libraryDescription" : "This library includes support for application components, user interface features, accessibility, data handling, network connectivity, and programming utilities."
"library_Timber_libraryDescription" : "A logger with a small, extensible API which provides utility on top of Android's normal Log class."
"library_WilliamChart_libraryDescription" : "Flexible charting library with nice motion capabilities."
"library_alexei_libraryDescription" : "Alexei is a type-face Image Processor that allows developers to easily perform calculations over images."
"library_androidBetterpickers_libraryDescription" : "DialogFragments modeled after the 4.2 Alarm Clock TimePicker to improve UX for picking time, date, and numbers."

"library_androidIconify_libraryDescription" : "Iconify allows you to include any of the 361 FontAwesome icons by Dave Gandy in your texts, your ActionBar, and even in your EditTexts. Icons are infinitely scalable, and customizable with shadows and everything you can do on texts."
"library_androidStyledDialogs_libraryDescription" : "Backport of material dialogs with easy-to-use API based on DialogFragment. This library makes styling and using dialogs a piece of cake."

"library_android_advancedrecyclerview_libraryDescription" : "This RecyclerView extension library provides Google's Inbox app like swiping, Play Music app like drag-and-drop sorting and expandable item features. Works on API level 9 or later."
"library_android_floating_action_button_libraryDescription" : "Yet another library for drawing Material Design promoted actions"
"library_android_gif_drawable_libraryDescription" : "Views and Drawable for displaying animated GIFs on Android"
"library_android_maps_utils_libraryDescription" : "This open-source library contains classes that are useful for a wide range of applications using the Google Maps Android API."
"library_android_platlogo_libraryDescription" : "The Easter Egg in the Android Settings App in Android Marshmallow, when you click multiple times on the version number. NOW CUSTOMIZABLE!"
"library_android_textview_linkbuilder_libraryDescription" : "Insanely easy way to create clickable links within a TextView."
"library_android_upload_service_libraryDescription" : "Easily upload files in the background with automatic Android Notification Center progress indication."

"library_androidannotations_libraryDescription" : "AndroidAnnotations is an Open Source framework that speeds up Android development. It takes care of the plumbing, and lets you concentrate on what's really important. By simplifying your code, it facilitates its maintenance."

"library_androidasyncservice_libraryDescription" : "AsyncService is born from an article I wrote a few weeks ago, which gave me a lot of feedbacks and interesting comments. AsyncService manages threading and caching transparently in your Android app. It is an alternative to AsyncTasks, Loaders, or more advanced libs like RxJava, Robospice, Groundy,… but AsyncService focuses on keeping your code short and simple!"
"library_androidcountrypicker_libraryDescription" : "CountryPicker is a simple fragment that can be embedded or shown as dialog. See the example to see more detail."
"library_androidflowlayout_libraryDescription" : "Extended linear layout that wrap its content when there is no place in the current line."

"library_androidroundcornerprogressbar_libraryDescription" : "Colorful progress bar with round corner on progress which you can customized a color and corner radius. A library has two type of progress bar."

"library_androidslidinguppanel_libraryDescription" : "Android Sliding Up Panel provides a simple way to add a draggable sliding up panel (popularized by Google Music, Google Maps and Rdio) to your Android application"

"library_androidviewhover_libraryDescription" : "A beautiful view to create a minimalistic hover effect over an ImageView"

"library_jodaTime_libraryDescription" : "Joda-Time is a date and time library that vastly improves on the JDK."
"library_ldialogs_libraryDescription" : "A small library replicating the new dialogs in android L."

"library_libphonenumber_libraryDescription" : "Google's common Java, C++ and Javascript library for parsing, formatting, storing and validating international phone numbers. The Java version is optimized for running on smartphones, and is used by the Android framework since 4.0 (Ice Cream Sandwich)"
"library_magisterjava_libraryDescription" : "A Java implementation of the Magister 6 API for desktop and Android."
"library_materialdialogs_libraryDescription" : "A beautiful, easy-to-use, and customizable dialogs API, enabling you to use Material designed dialogs down to API 8"
"library_materialedittext_libraryDescription" : "MaterialEditText, the EditText in Material Design, with more features that Google Material Design Spec has introduced."

"library_materialicons_libraryDescription" : "android-material-icons allows you to include any of the Material Design 1.0.1 icons by Google packed by Sergey Kupletsky in your texts, your ActionBar, and even in your EditTexts. Icons are infinitely scalable, and customizable with shadows and everything you can do on texts."

"library_materialmenu_libraryDescription" : "The library provides two wrappers of MaterialMenuDrawable that eases implementation into the ActionBar, NavigationDrawer slide interaction or into any other custom layout."
"library_mixpanelandroid_libraryDescription" : "Mixpanel is the most advanced analytics platform for mobile & web."
"library_moshi_libraryDescription" : "Moshi is a modern JSON library for Android and Java. It makes it easy to parse JSON into Java objects."

"library_mpandroidchart_libraryDescription" : "MPAndroidChart is a powerful and easy to use chart library for Android, supporting line-, bar-, scatter-, candlestick-, bubble-, pie- and radarcharts (spider web), as well as scaling, dragging (panning), selecting and animations."
"library_observablescrollview_libraryDescription" : "Android library to observe scroll events on scrollable views."
"library_okio_libraryDescription" : "Okio is a new library that complements java.io and java.nio to make it much easier to access, store, and process your data."
"library_paymill_libraryDescription" : "The Android SDK provides a flexible and easy to integrate payment solution for your Android applications."
"library_priorityjobqueue_libraryDescription" : "A Job Queue specifically written for Android to easily schedule jobs (tasks) that run in the background, improving UX and application stability."

"library_qcircledesigntemplate_libraryDescription" : "The LG QCircle design template library provides the layout designs and basic UI elements through API, enabling developers to save time designing and using repetitive tasks. The LG QCircle design template library provides various circle layouts and receives QuickCircle broadcast intents, adjusts layout position, and handles back button operation."
"library_qslide_libraryDescription" : "LG QSlide is the feature on LG smartphones to provide an application with multi-tasking using floating window and quick execution using Notification bar."
"library_reactivenetwork_libraryDescription" : "ReactiveNetwork is an Android library listening network connection state and Internet connectivity with RxJava Observables."

"library_rebound_libraryDescription" : "Rebound is a java library that models spring dynamics. Rebound spring models can be used to create animations that feel natural by introducing real world physics to your application."

"library_recyclerview_v7_libraryDescription" : "The recyclerview library adds the RecyclerView class. This class provides support for the RecyclerView widget, a view for efficiently displaying large data sets by providing a limited window of data items."
"library_recyclerviewanimators_libraryDescription" : "RecyclerView Animators is an Android library that allows developers to easily create RecyclerView with animations."
"library_retrolambda_libraryDescription" : "Backport of Java 8's lambda expressions to Java 7, 6 and 5"

"library_robotocalendarview_libraryDescription" : "Android Roboto Calendar View provides an easy and customizable calendar view with native support for the Roboto fonts, includes the brand new Roboto Slab fonts."
"library_rxJavaAndroid_libraryDescription" : "Reactive Extensions for the JVM – a library for composing asynchronous and event-based programs using observable sequences"

"library_rxandroid_libraryDescription" : "Android specific bindings for RxJava.

This module adds the minimum classes to RxJava that make writing reactive components in Android applications easy and hassle-free. More specifically, it provides a Scheduler that schedules on the main UI thread or any given Handler."

"library_rxjava_libraryDescription" : "RxJava is a Java VM implementation of Reactive Extensions: a library for composing asynchronous and event-based programs by using observable sequences.

It extends the observer pattern to support sequences of data/events and adds operators that allow you to compose sequences together declaratively while abstracting away concerns about things like low-level threading, synchronization, thread-safety and concurrent data structures."
"library_rxlifecycle_libraryDescription" : "The utilities provided here allow for automatic completion of sequences based on Activity or Fragment lifecycle events."
"library_side_menu_android_libraryDescription" : "Side menu with some categories to choose."
"library_simpleratingview_libraryDescription" : "A rating toggle for Android which switches between 3 rating levels: positive, neutral, and negative"
"library_smarttablayout_libraryDescription" : "A custom ViewPager title strip which gives continuous feedback to the user when scrolling"
"library_snackbar_libraryDescription" : "Library that implements Snackbars from Google's Material Design documentation."

"library_sticky_headers_recyclerview_libraryDescription" : "This decorator allows you to easily create section headers for RecyclerViews using a LinearLayoutManager in either vertical or horizontal orientation"
"library_stickylistheaders_libraryDescription" : "StickyListHeaders is an Android library that makes it easy to integrate section headers that stick to the top."
"library_stream_libraryDescription" : "Stream API from Java 8 rewrited on iterators for Java 7 and below."
"library_sugarorm_libraryDescription" : "Insanely easy way to work with Android databases."
"library_support_annotations_libraryDescription" : "The Annotation package provides APIs to support adding annotation metadata to your apps."

"library_support_v4_libraryDescription" : "This library is designed to be used with Android 1.6 (API level 4) and higher. It includes the largest set of APIs compared to the other libraries, including support for application components, user interface features, accessibility, data handling, network connectivity, and programming utilities."
"library_systembartint_libraryDescription" : "Apply background tinting to the Android system UI when using KitKat translucent modes."
"library_textdrawable_libraryDescription" : "TextDrawable is a Drawable object used to display text content and is intended for use on the Android mobile platform."
"library_volleyplus_libraryDescription" : "VolleyPlus library Project improvements to Volley along with full image caching"

playstore_details.title: OANN: Live Breaking News
playstore_details.description:
(Official) One America News Network delivers a credible source for national and international news, including breaking political, business and entertainment headlines.

***This is the Official OAN App, we are not affiliated with the other copy apps available in the store. Please download this app to make sure you are secured from any scams and that you get your credible news directly from the official source***

Features:
- Push Notifications for Breaking News & Top Stories
- Keep up to date 
- Breaking News Videos
- Ability to share the stories with friends and family
